. /* use principal factoring method because data is not multinormal */
. // estout with factor: http://repec.org/bocode/e/estout/advanced.html#advance
> d404
. 
. /* Uniqueness is the variance that is ‘unique’ to the variable and not shared
>  with other
> variables. It is equal to 1 – communality (variance that is shared with other
>  variables)
> Notice that the greater ‘uniqueness’ the lower the relevance of the variable 
> in the
> factor model. */
. 
